# Endevir licensing

This repository contains components under different licenses.

## Open-source components

Except for `apps/cloud`, the source code and documentation in this repository
are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

This includes the published Dart and Flutter packages under `packages/`, the
example application, schemas, scripts, documentation, and development
configuration. Each published package also carries its own copy of the license.

The complete license text is available at `LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt`.

## Endevir Cloud

The source code under `apps/cloud` is proprietary and is not licensed under
the Apache License, Version 2.0. See `apps/cloud/LICENSE`.

